{"tid":2504853,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"2021年，原生Android用家喜迎「回彈動畫」","createTime":"2021-04-26T07:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T09:48:33.000Z","uid":109923,"like":10,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"99539ec53e3e3f5475d2cb76101af4ddd579faf4","tid":2504853,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"An機碌到底/到頂冇回彈動畫，一直以嚟都係用邊緣陰影提醒<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYGPKJUshLur34QeqCQnvJg73VpCFp9YjsEX14HYpH81E?filename=B4A6UHZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4A6UHZ.png&h=dabc71fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2021年，原生Android 12終於有回彈動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSY7VFZCQCFZK2T8o5ZzNq94r53dfw2q3yS2MLVQwbMbP?filename=sXVbmn0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXVbmn0.gif&h=1760118c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ncontrol panel都有回彈動畫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQbFU6uei6Rbe94gqwCWb4oMovQWZkNfwFDdu29h9sePr?filename=NuJPSuF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNuJPSuF.gif&h=b49aaa78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上：新<br />\n下：舊<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWb3MxkLrK6ipW6EG2p6ZtMmtVXK9Vp92m7ivoXimDVHg?filename=ob2pGn0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fob2pGn0.gif&h=e3b08ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCustomized嘅Android都唔早得原生an幾多<br />\n2020年小米都係照住iOS抄先至有<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWkbdJoaUQhSpnzB63MnACeqt5x22YxQXTLj2WonoTXi9?filename=WkJoWYt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWkJoWYt.gif&h=23cbf929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n延伸閱讀<br />\n [山寨版iOS發佈會] 小米今次抄Apple抄得仲猖狂，痴撚線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2344348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2344348</a><br />\n<br />\n雀躍萬分的android用戶喜迎回彈動畫<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUfg14yPuRhLgqtRrAmCG76zFwqfZuMSMVAsrRHM5o8Tm?filename=MVUvB7m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVUvB7m.png&h=5eb1a980&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n然而....<br />\n就算Android系統本身有生動跟手嘅動畫又點？<br />\n啲垃圾Android App又未必有動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n120hz超順暢Android機快速滑動Youtube App，冇無回彈動畫，生硬地煞停等load片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(註：GIF得20fps)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQsY3nK3uMYXWHL6eWZmYyZBCCoTgUuhZdwe3KnLHuwBq?filename=jDyManq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjDyManq.gif&h=71f3d0e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niOS App成個頁面會跟隨手指向下拉，並以回彈動畫通知用家已重新整理<br />\nAndroid App只有一個轉圈圈提示<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTCthuJofoTG1iLhaC79givR4ZsdFL4jW3cqQ2KxFtDvC?filename=TTtwmt4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTtwmt4.gif&h=b37c9194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n所以可以預知，只要iPhone一出120hz，體驗一定好過An機<br />\n除咗系統本身有順暢、跟手、生動嘅原生動畫，仲包括使用iOS動畫api嘅iOS App<br />\n前者An廠可以整返靚啲動畫，後者生態問題可以話係完全無解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f095d2a9eddb85fa7228e06bdfa0b3c3751732c","tid":2504853,"uid":66365,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"唔覺ios 體驗好過an, 連熄個wifi 都勁撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d34717f35537bf9d9f06a70faf69d497e6418ca","tid":2504853,"uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5f095d2a9eddb85fa7228e06bdfa0b3c3751732c","tid":2504853,"uid":66365,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"唔覺ios 體驗好過an, 連熄個wifi 都勁撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"iPhone逼你開住wifi同bluetooth係為咗建立一個強大嘅lot生態<br />\n你睇下AirTag用咩嚟做定位<br />\n再了解下點解冇GPS嘅iPad出街都可以精準定位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5480abf0f193766cef6c47f6d22d82348d351ef8","tid":2504853,"uid":188176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:51:19.000Z","msg":"有無都唔緊要，反正都會disable番"},{"pid":"1f90f691d6aac4e5a6e0b401c6de7faed00b6746","tid":2504853,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:03:34.000Z","msg":"見到有人吹奏話Google轉用Fuchsia做智能電話OS就會順，真係得啖笑<br />\nFuchsia動畫唔做好，依然會係一pat屎<br />\n就算Fuchsia動畫做得好，啲App唔生性，體驗依然係差<br />\n<br />\n一個月前喺美國上市，目前市值50億美金嘅支那「新經濟」公司<br />\n佢嘅iOS app同An app嘅差距係如此巨大<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV2t3NpwoyiaVD8m4J5VPzvmxbLn2eWArXzz9b1TLr1Fm?filename=f3g6aGA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3g6aGA.gif&h=0f34b7c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdbGHGFLWkMc87tpFxfwixHNueLASE7aCBZ9R6FB4RhVe?filename=jKZzjzV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjKZzjzV.gif&h=c202d183&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nAndroid版完全冇動畫可言，啲UI閃嚟閃去<br />\n完全只係設計俾navigation bar用，反正冇手勢亦唔使跟手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(雖然手勢觸發返回功能，再播動畫都唔會係跟手，不過大mon機就易用好多)<br />\n<br />\nAndroid用家記得要感謝an版LIHKG居然有動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為市值50億美金嘅公司都未必有"},{"pid":"44a3668366cc98bd46c425bfeb2b676c8f00478e","tid":2504853,"uid":49781,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:23:52.000Z","msg":"發覺android用家真係好好耐性<br />\nifan一搵到位入android就一定入到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係anfan對ios咁遲先有多工頁同widgets就手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大方，難怪啲人話用android嘅智商平均高啲"},{"pid":"9a1b85e98546a567fcab5cec9ff660e08a61a9df","tid":2504853,"uid":176313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1d34717f35537bf9d9f06a70faf69d497e6418ca","tid":2504853,"uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5f095d2a9eddb85fa7228e06bdfa0b3c3751732c","tid":2504853,"uid":66365,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"唔覺ios 體驗好過an, 連熄個wifi 都勁撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"iPhone逼你開住wifi同bluetooth係為咗建立一個強大嘅lot生態<br />\n你睇下AirTag用咩嚟做定位<br />\n再了解下點解冇GPS嘅iPad出街都可以精準定位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"咪就係乜都逼住，咪麻撚煩咯"},{"pid":"d2e52645d13a39572ce9f09e96635084960ab2c2","tid":2504853,"uid":49781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d34717f35537bf9d9f06a70faf69d497e6418ca","tid":2504853,"uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5f095d2a9eddb85fa7228e06bdfa0b3c3751732c","tid":2504853,"uid":66365,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"唔覺ios 體驗好過an, 連熄個wifi 都勁撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"iPhone逼你開住wifi同bluetooth係為咗建立一個強大嘅lot生態<br />\n你睇下AirTag用咩嚟做定位<br />\n再了解下點解冇GPS嘅iPad出街都可以精準定位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"其實冇GPS可以精準定位呢<br />\n就唔關係咪ios事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nandroid都已經有呢個技術<br />\n但呢個世界有專利架嘛<br />\n唔係話做到就真係做出來嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caedaeab5f85ce0c8f4f1577980a42b6e010e969","tid":2504853,"uid":249708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f8a891b352775f2275ccf5a194498eae4107e3","tid":2504853,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44a3668366cc98bd46c425bfeb2b676c8f00478e","tid":2504853,"uid":49781,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:23:52.000Z","msg":"發覺android用家真係好好耐性<br />\nifan一搵到位入android就一定入到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係anfan對ios咁遲先有多工頁同widgets就手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大方，難怪啲人話用android嘅智商平均高啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"舊年iOS14出home screen嘅widget好多anfan笑喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我覺得佢哋太豬隊友啦，因為兩種widget根本唔係同一層次嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\niOS14可以搬出home screen只係閹割版，只有url api，VPN開關、計數機呢啲互動mini app功能係完全做唔到，原生股市app本來可以直接互動揀顯示實數定%<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家下下都開App先轉到，最慘係Apple仲要cut走舊嘅today extension widget<br />\n<br />\nAn機widget依然秒殺iOS14新版widget，當然iOS14可能只係要照顧細ram舊機，所以唔排除只係擠牙膏式改版重推<br />\n<br />\nbtw iOS個pip睇片同an機多工有好大段距離...除非你講緊iPadOS，雖然都係有距離"},{"pid":"eb3ab69d2d4a80ba02a96a998bfbad15c1ec2df3","tid":2504853,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30f8a891b352775f2275ccf5a194498eae4107e3","tid":2504853,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44a3668366cc98bd46c425bfeb2b676c8f00478e","tid":2504853,"uid":49781,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:23:52.000Z","msg":"發覺android用家真係好好耐性<br />\nifan一搵到位入android就一定入到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係anfan對ios咁遲先有多工頁同widgets就手下留情<img src=\"/ass